title: Central and Southern Afghanistan Household Income Generating Activities, May 2007
name: Central and Southern Afghanistan Household Income Generating Activities, May 2007
description:
This shapefile shows population and household income generating activities for districts in Central and Southern Afghanistan. The data comes from the Labor Markets, Livelihood Strategies, and Food Security in Afghanistan
A special report by the Famine Early Warning Systems Network (FEWS NET).

Data was uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
